### 1. Register DBlocker
POST http://localhost:8080/api/dblockers
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "1 Runway 13 Bandara",
    "serial_numb": "250001",
    "ip": "10.88.81.2",
    "latitude": -2.793327,
    "longitude": 122.131681,
    "desc": "Blocker 1 Runway 13 Bandara",
    "angle_start": 0
}

